# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Roadmap

> **The dependency-ordered task route** — the single ordered "what's next", independent of
> any chat context. Mirrors the tracker ({{TRACKER}}) so the plan survives outside it.
>
> **Protected:** the human owns the content. Agents perform **status-sync only**, and only via
> `/close-task` (Step 10). No agent reorders, adds, or removes route items on its own — it
> proposes a change and the human authorizes. When `{{TRACKER}}` is a real tracker, that
