## How to read this route

- Items are listed in **dependency order** — top to bottom is the intended execution sequence.
- "Blocked by" names the item(s) that must complete first. Never start a blocked item.
- One item = one ticket = one branch = one PR (the git-workflow rule).
- Tracker connection: `{{TRACKER}}` / org `{{TRACKER_ORG}}` / project `{{TRACKER_PROJECT}}` /
  prefix `{{TRACKER_KEY}}`. (Empty if the project runs on this local route only.)

